OL,6,FA teacher who "abused her role" and
OL,7,Ffailed to repay more than #28,000 of
OL,8,Floans to parents and colleagues at her
OL,9,Fschool has been banned from the
OL,10,Fprofession.
OL,12,FSusan Pletnick, who was a special
OL,13,Feducational needs co-ordinator
OL,14,F(Senco), borrowed money for flights to
OL,15,FSouth Africa, private healthcare, visa
OL,16,Fapplications and even a house deposit.
