OL,3,CTeacher spent #28,000 in loans from
OL,4,Cpupils' parents on flights and visa
OL,6,FThe 56-year-old loaned money from
OL,7,Fparents of pupils at Broughton Jewish
OL,8,FCassel Fox Primary School in Salford,
OL,9,Fa Teaching Regulation Agency (TRA)
OL,10,Fpanel concluded.
OL,12,FIn February 2018, parents of a pupil
OL,13,Fagreed to lend Mrs Pletnick money to
OL,14,Fenable her to travel to South Africa
OL,15,Fand they initially transferred her
OL,16,F#5,000 ` which she said she would
OL,17,Frepay.
