OL,3,CTeacher spent #28,000 in loans from
OL,4,Cpupils' parents on flights and visa
OL,6,FBut Mrs Pletnick then said her flights
OL,7,Fhad been cancelled and she needed more
OL,8,Fmoney to travel so the parents lent a
OL,9,Ffurther #4,440, the panel heard.
OL,11,FAnother time in 2018, the teacher told
OL,12,Fthem she needed to pay #12,800 in
OL,13,Fconnection with a visa application
OL,14,Fotherwise she would have to return to
OL,15,FSouth Africa, so the parents lent her
OL,16,Fthe full amount.
