OL,6,FMrs Pletnick, who worked at Broughton
OL,7,FJewish Cassel Fox Primary School
OL,8,Fbetween April 2013 and April 2019,
OL,9,Falso borrowed around #4,000 from a
OL,10,Fcolleague which was not repaid.
OL,12,FMrs Pletnick informed her colleague
OL,13,Fthat she was moving but did not have
OL,14,Fmoney to pay for a deposit and her
OL,15,Fcolleague offered to help her.
