OL,6,FIn 2016, the school also lent Mrs
OL,7,FPletnick thousands of pounds from the
OL,8,Fschool's charity account to support
OL,9,Fher expenses in staying within the
OL,10,Fcountry, and around #4,000 remained
OL,11,Foutstanding, the panel heard.
OL,13,FMrs Pletnick said she had no money and
OL,14,Fwas "desperate" and this led her to
OL,15,Fask people for help and accept money
OL,16,Ffrom people when it was offered.
