OL,6,FThe tribunal concluded that the
OL,7,Fconduct of Mrs Pletnick "fell
OL,8,Fsignificantly short of the standards
OL,9,Fexpected" and banned her from the
OL,10,Fteaching profession with a review
OL,11,Fperiod of three years.
