OL,6,FRuling on behalf of the Education
OL,7,FSecretary, Sarah Buxcey said: "The
OL,8,Ffindings of misconduct are serious as
OL,9,Fthey include a finding of obtaining
OL,10,Fmoney from the school, parents and
OL,11,Fcolleagues, failing to repay, conduct
OL,12,Fthat amounted to an abuse of her role
OL,13,Fas a teacher and Senco and conduct
OL,14,Fthat lacked integrity and was
OL,15,Fdishonest."
